Titolo: FS1 Flight Simulator

Anno: 1979

Descrizione: FS1 Flight Simulator is a 1979 video game published by Sublogic for the Apple II. A TRS-80 version followed in 1980. FS1 Flight Simulator is a flight simulator in the cockpit of a slightly modernized Sopwith Camel. FS1 is the first in a line of simulations from Sublogic which, beginning in 1982, were also sold by Microsoft as Microsoft Flight Simulator.
Sublogic later released updated versions for both the Apple II and TRS-80 on 5 1‚ÅÑ4 inch diskettes. The updates include enhanced terrain, help menus, and a bomb sight.